MAE_slice_sCT_QA.display_name: [T1w MRI-to-CT MAE prediction] [Brain] FedSynthCT MRI-T1w 2D MAE prediction
MAE_slice_sCT_QA.description: This module allows to predict the conversion error of a synthetic CT.The prediction value is referred to each axial slice. The model was trained using data from FedSynthCT-Brain, a federated learning framework for brain MRI-to-CT translation.
